  "description": "愛爾蘭哲學家（1685—1753）",
  "bio": "喬治·柏克萊（英語：George Berkeley，1685年3月12日—1753年1月14日），英裔愛爾蘭哲學家，同時為聖公會駐愛爾蘭科克郡克洛因鎮的主教，與約翰·洛克和大衛·休謨被認為是英國近代經驗主義哲學家中的三大代表人物，因捍衛、推動主觀唯心主義而聞名。\n柏克萊是一位涉獵廣泛的思想家，對宗教（這是他哲學動機的根本）、視覺心理學、數學、物理學、倫理學、經濟學和醫學都有興趣。著有《視覺新論》（1709年）、《希拉斯與菲洛努斯之間的三次對話》與《人類知識原理》（1710年）等作品。\n美國加州的柏克萊市便是以他的名字命名。耶魯大學也有一個本科寄宿學院柏克萊學院是以他命名。",
  "bio_source": "zhwiki",
  "description_en": "Irish idealist philosopher and Anglican bishop (1685–1753)",
  "bio_en": "George Berkeley ( BARK-lee; 12 March 1685 – 14 January 1753), known as Bishop Berkeley (Bishop of Cloyne of the Anglican Church of Ireland), was an Anglo-Irish philosopher, writer, and clergyman who is regarded as the founder of immaterialism, a philosophical theory he developed which later came to be known as subjective idealism. He has also been called \"the father of idealism\" by German philosopher Arthur Schopenhauer. Berkeley played a leading role in the empiricism movement and was one of its pioneers.",
  "bio_en_source": "enwiki"
}